<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><meta charset="UTF-8"></head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #4C4C4C;">

<p>Dear anh <%- managerName %>,</p>
<p>
  Tôi là: <strong><%- name %></strong><br>
  Bộ phận: <strong><%- department %></strong>
</p>
<p>Tôi gửi mail này để xin anh/chị xác nhận giúp tôi thông tin timesheet như sau:</p>

<ul style="padding-left: 20px;">
<% violations.forEach(function(v) { %>
  <li>
    <strong><%- formatDate(v.record.date) %></strong> (<%- v.weekdayVi %>): <%- describe(v) %><br>
    <em>Nguyên nhân thiếu thông tin: <%- reason %></em>
  </li>
<% }); %>
</ul>

<p>
  Mong anh xác nhận giúp tôi để bộ phận Nhân sự note lại.<br>
  Xin cảm ơn
</p>

<br>
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-spacing:0; border-collapse:collapse; color:#444; width:400px; font-size:10pt; font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">
  <tr>
    <td colspan="2" style="padding:0;">
      <span style="font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000;"><%- name %> (Mr.)</span>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan="2" style="padding:5px 0 0;">
      <strong style="color:#F1C232; font-family:Arial,sans-serif;"><%- department %> Department</strong>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan="2" style="padding:0;">&nbsp;</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" style="padding:0 15px 0 0; border-right:1px solid #FFC20F;">
      <img src="https://hblab.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Logo-M.png" width="162" alt="HBLab" style="display:block; max-width:162px;">
    </td>
    <td valign="top" style="padding:0 0 0 15px;">
      <% if (phone) { %><strong>Tel:&nbsp;<%- phone %></strong><br><% } %>
      <strong>Web:</strong>&nbsp;<a href="https://hblab.vn/" style="color:#1A50B7;">https://hblab.vn/</a><br>
      <strong>Add:</strong>&nbsp;219 Trung Kinh Street, Cau Giay District, Hanoi, Vietnam
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<br>
<p style="color:#FF0000; font-size:11px;">
  This email contains strictly confidential information. If you are not the intended recipient,
  please notify the sender immediately. Any form of copying, distribution, or sharing of the
  email's content, whether accidental or intentional, is strictly prohibited and may be unlawful.
</p>

</body>
</html>
